Under ubuntu, make rpm package for icamerasrc.

*****************************************************
Prerequisite for build RPM package:

Install rpmbuild under ubuntu if needed,
sudo apt-get install rpm

Install auto-make utils needed for building the rpm from source,
sudo apt-get install autoconf libtool

*****************************************************
Build RPM for icamerasrc:

Run the shell script under this directory to build and package rpm.

./build_rpm.sh

*****************************************************
Install icamerasrc RPM to target host:

sudo rpm -ivh --nodeps --noparentdirs --prefix `pkg-config --variable=pluginsdir gstreamer-1.0` icamerasrc-*.rpm

or

sudo rpm -ivh --nodeps  --prefix `pkg-config --variable=pluginsdir gstreamer-1.0` icamerasrc-*.rpm
